Bookmark an Insight in a Model

You can export a bookmarked insight to Quip. It also makes it easier to find in the Insights List when the Bookmark filter on the toolbar is disabled.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

If you click the Bookmark Filter icon on the Model toolbar to enable it, the Insights list displays only those insights that have been bookmarked.

To bookmark an insight, click its Bookmark icon to enable it. The color changes to blue.
To undo the bookmark for an insight, click its Bookmark icon again to disable it. The color changes to white.
title: Bookmarking Insights in Salesforce Analytics
